In the game Railroad crossing you will regulate automobile traffic.

At first sight it is not a difficult task but requires attention and the ability to assess the situation. Game Railroad crossing, will teach you the skills regulator. Crossroads has 2 crossing gates that you need to adjust the car traffic. On the approximation and the direction of the train will signal yellow arrows. Your task is to calculate the time needed for that would all transport safely crossed the railway crossing, for a time to open or close the gate for you to decide. All in your hands!
